item.title: How Do I Spawn Hay Bales And All?
item.dc:creator: @firespell firespell
item.description:
@firespell wrote:

In client.java search for case 121: Then under it put
makeGlobalObject(XPOS,YPOS,OBJECTID,ROTATION,10);

Hay bales id is 298/299
This is for rotation 0= WEST | -1 = NORTH | -2 = EAST | -3 = SOUTH
Youll need to find XPOS and YPOS yourself (this is the square you want the objects on.)
